<div class="w3-content w3-container w3-padding-64" id="papersubmission">
	<h2 class="w3-center">PAPER SUBMISSION</h2>
<div class="w3-padding-large">
	<p>The authors are invited to send their papers to the <BR>
Email: aueceicon@gmail.com<BR><br>
	The papers must be submitted through Email only. Papers must be written in English and should be at least SIX pages in total and must conform to IEEE format. The authors will be notified on the status of the paper acceptance through Email. Authors can view IEEE template at www.ieee.org. A blind peer-review process will be used to evaluate all the submitted papers. Papers are reviewed on the basis that they do not contain plagiarized material and have not been submitted to any other conference at the same time (double submission). 
	At least one of the author's of the accepted paper is required to register for the conference and present the paper at the conference. Non-refundable registration fees must be paid prior to the due date of registration. For authors with multiple accepted papers, one registration for each paper is required. Accepted and presented papers will be in the conference proceedings. For further assistance, author's mobile number may be intimated.
</p>
</div>
</div>

